{"tid":2500749,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"再開 提防傳銷 勿填問卷","createTime":"2021-04-23T01:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T17:30:02.000Z","uid":364447,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd52585e5f17382f9d316522ccc12d977cc43d8e","tid":2500749,"uid":364447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:39:36.000Z","msg":"如題 年年都有傳銷喺Dse考場叫你填問卷呃你電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後考完就趁你徬徨call你讀垃圾學校（指南針大學 hkue TAFE等）或者過多幾年扮叫你見工做傳銷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有野都由你好心幫佢做問卷比左電話開始 所以千祈唔好填或者填假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway Dse加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱見到上埋蘋果<br />\n[url]https://<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210423/7GBYBH4OHFHJXNBCKO4HXB4NOM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3m10rZis0TG1vHhj-U2XDnmU-gBkeJdqPjy5GkbEcqBviB2O_0IvXIOfQ[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2F7GBYBH4OHFHJXNBCKO4HXB4NOM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3m10rZis0TG1vHhj-U2XDnmU-gBkeJdqPjy5GkbEcqBviB2O_0IvXIOfQ%5B%2Furl%5D&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBraDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=4708de74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2F7GBYBH4OHFHJXNBCKO4HXB4NOM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3m10rZis0TG1vHhj-U2XDnmU-gBkeJdqPjy5GkbEcqBviB2O_0IvXIOfQ%5B%2Furl%5D&h=511d90dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.appledaily.co